    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nIn https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/020eb69722, a call to `Throwable.initClause` is removed. This fixes an issue where the driver can hang during a broadcast exchange that throws an OOM error.\r\n\r\nWe have similar code that calls `initClause` in `org.apache.spark.sql.rapids.execution.GpuBroadcastExchangeExecBase#createOutOfMemoryException`, so we should check to see if we need to make a similar change.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nReview code to determine if we should make the same change.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\n\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n",
